<h1>Typography Tokens</h1>

<p>Font size and font family tokens that define the typographic scale of the NYS Design System. Click the copy button next to any token to copy it as a <code>var()</code> expression.</p>

<h2 id="font-size">Font Size</h2>
<p>A nine-step type scale from <code>2xs</code> to <code>9xl</code>. Components reference these tokens internally — use them in your own CSS to stay aligned with the system's typographic rhythm.</p>
<div class="token-list">
{% for token in collections.tokens["font-size"] %}
  {% include "partials/token-item.njk" %}
{% endfor %}
</div>

<h2 id="font-family">Font Family</h2>
<p>The typeface stacks used across NYSDS components and page-level typography. See <a href="/foundations/typography/">Typography</a> for installation and usage guidance.</p>
